# .cursorrules
- Enforce version control: changes must reference /docs/infra-runbook.md version tag.
- Never insert secrets, tokens, or keys.
- Keep S3 private via CloudFront OAC; no public ACLs.
- Follow directory layout: public/, .github/workflows/, docs/, scripts/.
- Prefer PR-based edits on content/* branches; no direct pushes to master.
- Use ChatGPT only for content/draft generation, not secret handling or deployment keys.
